properties.areaDesc: Sacramento Mountains Above 7500 Feet; East Slopes Sacramento Mountains Below 7500 Feet; Southern Gila Highlands/Black Range
properties.senderName: NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 27 at 2:02PM MST until January 28 at 1:00AM MST by NWS El Paso TX/Santa Teresa NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Across the peaks and eastern slopes of the Sacramento
Mountains and Blacks Range.

* WHEN...Until 1 AM MST Tuesday.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Winds will gradually decrease during the
early morning hours Tuesday to 15 to 25 mph by sunrise.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 AM MST TUESDAY
